a_r = \sqrt{a^2-a_t^2} = \sqrt{(2.2)^2-(1.5)^2} \frac{\text{m}}{\text{sec}^2} \approx 1.6 \frac{\text{m}}{\text{sec}^2} 
a_r = \frac{v^2}{r} \implies v = \sqrt{a_r r} \approx 15.5 \frac{\text{m}}{\text{sec}}
d = \frac12 a_t t^2
