v = a_t t
d = \frac{v^2}{2 a_t} = \frac{a_r r}{2 a_t}
\theta = d/r
\theta = \frac{a_r}{2 a_t} = \frac12 \sqrt{\frac{a^2}{a_t^2}-1} \approx 0.536 \, \text{rad} \approx 30.7^{\circ}
